{
  "stem": "11998.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And once you were outside the ghetto, you were told that, you know, you would be subject to being shot on-site.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So that was a very serious offense to go to.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "As a matter of factor, at one point I was going to escape.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so I went ahead, and I got some peroxide.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And put some peroxide in a basin.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I put it on my hair to make myself blonde.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I was going to escape out of the ghetto with some of the guys.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I must have put too much peroxide because my hair became yellow like straw.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it was a feeble attempt.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then, of course, everybody discouraged us from going because if they caught you-- there was nowhere to go.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That was the biggest problem, that there was nowhere to go.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You didn't know if you went outside of the ghetto, if a Pol that saw you wouldn't denounce you and take you to the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And if they did, they either sent you away, or they shot you on site.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So it was very difficult.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, there are many people who escaped.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Especially some of my sister's friends.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were young Zionists.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they banded together, and they escaped one at a time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know what happened to them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I saw people being shot.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well this already while they were deporting us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And if somebody went out from one line to the other line-- if they were trying to run from one place to the other-- they just took a little revolver and shot them on the spot.",
      "word_count": 36
    }
  ],
